agentData.mission: Create a deterministic artifact verification step that asserts runtime/_build contains non-empty required outputs (at minimum: one JSON report in runtime/_build/reports, one CSV table in runtime/_build/tables, one PNG/PDF figure in runtime/_build/figures, and one log in runtime/_build/logs). The verifier should fail with a clear missing-file list and be runnable as a single command.
